{
  "stem": "13258.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "By then, we had heard the rumors that, from the city, [INAUDIBLE], where my mother was, they had evacuated people in this direction of the Lithuanian border, of Wilno.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "So now we're not trying anymore to go there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "We're trying to go in the direction of Wilno.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And our schedule, our map, shows us that from Zbarazh, there is no train.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "But there is a town, again, known in Polish, [INAUDIBLE] from there, there is a train connection in the direction of Wilno.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the seven of us hire two farmers-- unbeknownst to us, Ukrainians.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they agreed, for a lot of money, to take us to Zbarazh.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was one nightmarish ride at night in the dark, with people whom we didn't know, where we didn't know that there were Ukrainian bands in the forest over there, and where the roads were not roads.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This is a piece of dirt.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And when it rains, you probably can't drive through.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's like something like people were going in the Wild West in America years ago.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "At one point at night, the horses stopped.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There must've been some bridge, or something, a little stream.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In any case, we got into [INAUDIBLE] in the wee morning hours.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And here suddenly, they dropped us at the edge of the town and went back.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Luckily, they neither robbed nor killed us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then there is a stream of vehicles, civilian and military, going through, which later out, we found out was the Polish government running, and the general's staff running away to Romania.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mm-hmm.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, first of all, in [INAUDIBLE], we went, we went to sleep in the evening.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And before we went to sleep, a military motorcycle had stopped and called my father's name-- the guy who was riding it.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
